hondo717: |cp||at|Now as to Lebensohl. It is a complicated convention, and I don't recommend you play it if you play strong NT. I recommend you use "stolen bid" doubles and systems on if you play strong NT and there is interference. However, playing the weak NT, where there is often interference, I have found Lebensohl works well. Without getting into too much detail, let me describe a few of the basics of Lebensohl.|
